name: Total Green Solutions
overview:
Profile: Established in the year 2006, at Delhi, (India), we “Total Green Solutions”, are one of the leading providers of Landscaping, Development and Maintenance services. The offered range of services includes Landscaping Maintenance, Commercial Landscaping, Residential Landscaping, Vertical Garden Landscaping, Terrace Garden Landscaping services.

Our USP: Our organization has gained recognition in the domestic market for offering high quality Landscaping, Development and Maintenance services. Some major factors instrumental in making us the preferred choice of our clients are:

Our Quality: Since the inception, we have been providing our clients a qualitative array of Printing Landscaping, Development and Maintenance services, which sets us apart from our counterparts in the industry. These services are planned and executed in complete compliance with the international standards of eminence.

Our Team

We have recruited a talented team of professionals, who work close co-ordination with clients in order to fulfill their wide demands. Our professionals are selected by us after thorough analysis of their skills and knowledge in the respective domains.

Client Satisfaction

As a client-oriented organization, we have been able to successfully attain maximum level of client contentment by providing optimum quality services. We assure that the services are rendered as per the needs of the clients within promised time frame in order to meet client’s exact requirements. In order to attain maximum client satisfaction..
